				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Most effective training for a Young Bard<a name="54404"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 30 04 8:21 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I am a Bard returning to EQ after a 2 1/2 year layoff.
<br />

<br />
I have been reading some of the guides and see all of the information on swarm kiting, and wondered if this is what I should be training to do (if I plan on playing in later levels) or am I better off doing what I have been doing (single pull, tank w/4 song twist).
<br />

<br />
What will serve me the best in the long run?  Speed of leveling is not a major concern for me.
<br />

<br />
Sotovoce (Crooner of 22 Songs)</span></td>
