				<td colspan="2"><span>Soto, 
<br />

<br />
I would suggest that you group.  The nice thing about LDoN is that it starts at level 20.  You can get yerself a young group in yer 20s and have some real fun.  The LDoN dungeons are really very interestiing, especially since you've been away for so long.
<br />

<br />
And, as mentioned above, you won't be able to melee solo much longer.  Personally, I NEVER solo anymore because I find it boring.  I much prefer groups. 
<br />

<br />
Anyway, have fun and welcome back.
<br />

<br />
Wyndaria,
