				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Most effective training for a Young Bard<a name="55211"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 5 04 12:21 AM</span></td>
