				<td colspan="2"><span>The most effective training for ANY bard is grouping and being the puller.
<br />

<br />
This is what you are!  You are an awesome part of any group, you will regularly be the one that keeps the group alive.  You will be able to handle situations that any other class would wipe in or take 5 times as long.
<br />

<br />
Your ability to solo might seem amazing but the more you group the more you will realise that grouping is the place you REALLY shine.
<br />

<br />
Just remember, if you pull off some amazing trick or pull and you are soloing nobody will know, if you are in a group you get... well you get groupies!   A true bard should seek adulation and fame!
<br />

<br />
Melo</span></td>
