				<td colspan="2"><span>Last night the cleric in my group in a Ldon adventure told me I could be anyone in this group(tank, puller, CC). I mentioned that I couldn't be the healer and we both had a good laugh.
<br />

<br />
As a Bard your main job is to be a Puller. Don't solo so much, learn to be the best puller you can be.
<br />

<br />
A few seasons back on my server there is not alot of people so what happened we made a group with 3 bards, Tank, Backstabber, and Healer. We lost due to the entire group going LD within a 5 minute area of time, but that was one of the best times I have had.
<br />

<br />
Just my 2 cents
<br />

<br />
Jaimesy Hetfield</span></td>
